WEBVTT

01:43.289 --> 01:46.090
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.130 --> 01:48.900
[Episode 16]

01:56.020 --> 01:57.100
Liu Yujie.

02:02.420 --> 02:03.020
Jing.

02:07.820 --> 02:09.060
Have you seen Wang Qiang?

02:10.830 --> 02:11.880
Yes.

02:12.410 --> 02:13.830
Then why didn't you contact me?

02:14.300 --> 02:16.350
Jing, didn't you say...

02:16.560 --> 02:17.940
I should wait for you to contact me

02:18.590 --> 02:19.750
for matters regarding Wang Qiang?

02:20.010 --> 02:20.870
Cut the crap.

02:21.070 --> 02:21.790
What did he say?

02:23.430 --> 02:24.190
He said...

02:25.790 --> 02:26.670
to wait a little more.

02:27.079 --> 02:27.810
To wait a little more?

02:28.020 --> 02:29.380
How long have we been waiting?

02:29.620 --> 02:30.910
I don't know.

02:31.210 --> 02:32.020
He said...

02:32.590 --> 02:34.940
things are tense lately,

02:35.320 --> 02:36.450
so it's difficult to get done.

02:36.670 --> 02:37.670
Difficult to get done?

02:37.920 --> 02:39.800
Or is it difficult to get done because there's not enough money?

02:40.150 --> 02:40.910
Tell him

02:40.970 --> 02:42.350
I’ll give him how ever much he wants.

02:42.829 --> 02:44.940
Get him to deal with Lu Yan as soon as possible.

02:45.970 --> 02:46.860
Jing.

02:48.340 --> 02:49.090
How about...

02:50.150 --> 02:51.390
you don't get Wang Qiang

02:51.390 --> 02:52.740
to go after Lu Yan?

02:53.510 --> 02:54.550
What do you mean?

02:54.910 --> 02:55.980
I...I...

02:56.030 --> 02:57.290
I didn't mean that.

02:57.470 --> 02:59.260
What I mean is,

02:59.380 --> 03:01.580
we've been classmates for so many years.

03:01.910 --> 03:03.010
We are friends.

03:03.200 --> 03:04.780
By doing this,

03:04.930 --> 03:06.820
what will happen if the police caught Wang Qiang?

03:10.870 --> 03:11.630
I don’t like it

03:11.670 --> 03:13.260
when others teach me how to do things.

03:14.630 --> 03:15.230
Jing.

03:16.230 --> 03:17.370
I'm sorry.

03:18.020 --> 03:19.579
That's not what I meant.

03:20.350 --> 03:21.320
Jing, I'm sorry.

03:22.070 --> 03:23.300
I'm sorry.

03:26.670 --> 03:28.579
Aren't you my good friend?

03:28.990 --> 03:30.450
If I go to jail,

03:31.310 --> 03:32.870
wouldn't you come with me?

03:42.380 --> 03:44.930
Why are my new shoes dirty again?

04:06.670 --> 04:07.700
How despicable.

04:19.269 --> 04:22.010
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

04:22.110 --> 04:24.240
From pretending to be Deng Man,

04:25.190 --> 04:26.530
and then Wang Qianqian,

04:26.380 --> 04:31.850
[Deng Man] [Wang Qianqian] [Chanson Artificial Lake]

04:26.560 --> 04:28.650
and then dying in the same lake as Deng Man.

04:28.910 --> 04:30.210
Then we have Wang Qiang,

04:30.540 --> 04:32.030
who has been stalking, taking photos secretly,

04:31.860 --> 04:32.930
[Ding Jing] [Lu Yan]

04:32.190 --> 04:33.040
and even attempted rape.

04:33.150 --> 04:34.230
All these incidents

04:34.900 --> 04:35.990
point back to Lu Yan.

04:37.020 --> 04:38.010
So now,

04:38.140 --> 04:39.190
the prime suspect

04:39.430 --> 04:40.200
is Ding Jing.

04:40.630 --> 04:41.310
It's pretty obvious

04:41.390 --> 04:42.340
that it was Ding Jing who

04:42.390 --> 04:43.210
asked Wang Qiang to

04:43.320 --> 04:44.350
take photos of Lu Yan secretly.

04:44.550 --> 04:46.230
What I can't figure out now is

04:46.230 --> 04:48.750
what is the mastermind's purpose

04:48.770 --> 04:49.810
behind Wang Qianqian's murder?

04:50.240 --> 04:50.890
Why?

04:51.370 --> 04:52.130
Look.

04:53.210 --> 04:54.610
There is a clear motive and purpose

04:55.240 --> 04:57.270
to kill Wang Qianqian.

04:57.790 --> 04:58.850
It's to bring Lu Yan

04:58.930 --> 05:00.980
[Ding Jing] [Lu Yan]

04:59.030 --> 05:00.830
back to the fear she felt at the time.

05:01.190 --> 05:02.660
Consistently

05:02.680 --> 05:03.550
and repeatedly,

05:03.700 --> 05:04.650
they kept bringing her more pain

05:04.790 --> 05:05.470
and regret.

05:06.030 --> 05:07.890
If we consider Wang Qiang,

05:08.520 --> 05:10.060
his methods are very straightforward.

05:11.350 --> 05:12.140
Secretly taking photos,

05:12.790 --> 05:13.620
and stalking.

05:13.690 --> 05:14.840
His purpose

05:15.280 --> 05:16.640
is to physically hurt Lu Yan

05:16.680 --> 05:17.830
and also tarnish Lu Yan's reputation.

05:18.790 --> 05:19.990
It seems that their modus operandi

05:19.990 --> 05:21.350
is completely different.

05:21.750 --> 05:22.950
So, you believe that

05:22.990 --> 05:24.320
the criminal motives

05:24.350 --> 05:25.550
behind these two cases

05:25.580 --> 05:26.430
are completely different?

05:26.450 --> 05:27.050
Yes.

05:28.240 --> 05:29.370
I don't think so.

05:29.640 --> 05:31.610
Ding Jing's personality is flawed.

05:31.900 --> 05:34.540
If she can order Wang Qiang to hurt Lu Yan,

05:34.880 --> 05:36.500
she can also get others to do the same.

05:36.810 --> 05:38.700
You are college alumni, right?

05:39.390 --> 05:40.280
This proves

05:40.310 --> 05:42.150
she knows

05:42.230 --> 05:43.230
about Deng Man's suicide.

05:43.350 --> 05:44.310
And Ding Jing

05:44.350 --> 05:45.360
definitely can afford

05:45.390 --> 05:46.390
to hire a hitman.

05:47.400 --> 05:48.850
As I recall, information showed that

05:48.990 --> 05:50.600
after Deng Man's accident,

05:50.630 --> 05:51.940
Ding Jing went abroad.

05:54.830 --> 05:55.430
By the way,

05:55.480 --> 05:56.730
what about Liu Yujie?

05:56.750 --> 05:58.620
Is she aware of Ding Jing's

05:58.650 --> 05:59.409
actions?

05:59.460 --> 06:00.670
Wang Qiang

06:00.970 --> 06:01.810
was

06:02.180 --> 06:03.210
introduced to Ding Jing

06:03.360 --> 06:04.670
by Liu Yujie.

06:05.900 --> 06:07.210
But it was only much later

06:07.510 --> 06:08.910
when she found out what Ding Jing

06:08.940 --> 06:10.100
asked Wang Qiang to do.

06:11.680 --> 06:12.830
What about Wang Qiang?

06:13.140 --> 06:14.400
I interrogated Wang Qiang.

06:15.250 --> 06:17.570
He’s a voyeuristic photographer

06:18.590 --> 06:19.960
who sells photos of girls.

06:20.870 --> 06:22.130
Looking at the way he acts,

06:23.270 --> 06:24.350
he's unlikely to be a killer.

06:27.380 --> 06:29.940
If it was Ding Jing who ordered Wang Qiang

06:29.970 --> 06:31.070
to hurt Lu Yan

06:31.090 --> 06:32.630
and kill Wang Qianqian,

06:32.790 --> 06:34.690
it indeed does not add up.

06:35.720 --> 06:37.960
Ding Jing can definitely afford

06:37.990 --> 06:39.880
to hire a hitman to commit the crime.

06:40.170 --> 06:40.950
Why would she find

06:40.990 --> 06:41.909
someone like Wang Qiang?

06:42.670 --> 06:44.150
His counter-investigation skills are weak,

06:44.180 --> 06:45.430
and he's easily discovered.

06:45.950 --> 06:46.790
Wouldn't this make it even easier

06:46.820 --> 06:47.590
to expose herself,

06:47.909 --> 06:48.570
no?

06:50.700 --> 06:51.680
So,

06:52.000 --> 06:53.820
Ding Jing is not the only person

06:53.950 --> 06:54.940
who is targeting

06:54.960 --> 06:55.980
Lu Yan.

06:57.650 --> 06:59.310
If so, how are they related?

07:01.000 --> 07:02.460
That I don't know.

07:02.820 --> 07:04.010
But this person

07:05.060 --> 07:06.780
is much smarter than Ding Jing.

07:18.840 --> 07:19.500
Lu.

07:22.660 --> 07:24.340
Xiaoman's surgery time is confirmed.

07:24.390 --> 07:25.890
It's the day after tomorrow at 2 p.m.

07:26.360 --> 07:27.750
I have also informed her family.

07:27.790 --> 07:28.550
But Mrs. Lin

07:28.580 --> 07:29.950
still looks very worried.

07:30.740 --> 07:32.510
Actually, this is not a major surgery.

07:32.530 --> 07:33.870
It's just that Xiaoman's mood has been poor.

07:34.030 --> 07:35.700
Keep an eye on her for the next two days.

07:36.150 --> 07:36.909
Don't worry.

07:37.110 --> 07:38.070
Mood is one of the

07:38.120 --> 07:39.310
important indications for surgery.

07:40.110 --> 07:40.510
Don't worry.

07:40.550 --> 07:41.930
I'll continue to talk to them.

07:42.110 --> 07:42.830
Thank you.

07:44.960 --> 07:45.750
You're now off duty.

07:45.790 --> 07:46.430
Don't just zone out here

07:46.430 --> 07:47.070
all by yourself.

07:47.070 --> 07:47.950
Go home now.

07:48.990 --> 07:50.270
Are you working the night shift today?

07:51.300 --> 07:52.510
Well, I'm single.

07:52.540 --> 07:53.840
The night shift specialist

07:54.130 --> 07:54.810
has to be me.

07:56.610 --> 07:57.320
Bye.

08:15.330 --> 08:16.690
You still have work to do?

08:17.930 --> 08:18.700
It's nothing.

08:19.640 --> 08:21.230
Do you know some celebrity

08:21.310 --> 08:22.950
named Yu Bofeng?

08:24.190 --> 08:25.240
I don't know what's wrong with him,

08:25.270 --> 08:26.710
but he has been insistent on learning criminal psychology from me.

08:26.990 --> 08:27.800
He calls me every day.

08:28.990 --> 08:29.610
Senior.

08:29.750 --> 08:30.270
Senior!

08:32.070 --> 08:33.440
Someone found a female tenant

08:33.470 --> 08:34.630
in the suburbs of Xishan

08:34.870 --> 08:36.270
who looks very similar to the murderer of

08:36.270 --> 08:36.980
Wang Qianqian.

08:37.419 --> 08:38.120
Bring a team. Let's go.

08:38.159 --> 08:38.669
Go.

08:38.740 --> 08:40.070
I won't go with you all.

08:40.150 --> 08:40.770
Yes, don't come.

08:40.870 --> 08:41.520
I'm leaving.

08:43.230 --> 08:45.000
After all this time, you’re not even going to buy me a meal?

08:45.280 --> 08:46.060
Order takeout.

08:46.100 --> 08:47.100
I'll reimburse it for you.

08:47.680 --> 08:54.370
[Physical Fitness Center]

08:55.430 --> 08:56.280
Liu Yujie.

08:59.950 --> 09:00.900
Lu Yan?

09:03.380 --> 09:04.730
W-Why are you here?

09:14.910 --> 09:15.820
[Ninghai International Cultural and Artwork Exchange Conference]

09:21.270 --> 09:22.230
Okay, look here.

09:22.260 --> 09:23.670
Look here.

09:23.710 --> 09:24.740
Look here.

09:24.880 --> 09:26.260
Please look at the camera. Thank you.

09:26.280 --> 09:27.490
Look at the camera.

09:27.790 --> 09:28.710
Look at the camera, please.

09:28.710 --> 09:29.510
Great. One more.

09:35.430 --> 09:36.960
Mr. Yu Bofeng,

09:37.030 --> 09:37.710
why did you agree to

09:37.750 --> 09:38.780
this endorsement?

09:38.870 --> 09:40.030
Because I was already

09:40.110 --> 09:41.590
familiar with this brand.

10:01.450 --> 10:02.670
Hello, Jing.

10:02.690 --> 10:03.670
Liu Yujie, where have you been?

10:03.670 --> 10:04.450
So slow.

10:05.170 --> 10:06.390
I-I'm here.

10:06.410 --> 10:07.310
Where are you?

10:07.360 --> 10:08.570
I'm in the dressing room upstairs.

10:08.610 --> 10:09.340
Come up.

10:09.640 --> 10:10.830
Okay, I'm coming.

10:17.510 --> 10:18.810
You tugged on my hair.

10:20.000 --> 10:21.830
I-I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

10:22.050 --> 10:22.870
It's a great day.

10:22.910 --> 10:23.830
I don't want to lose my temper with you.

10:23.870 --> 10:24.910
Why are you so clumsy?

10:26.380 --> 10:27.850
What did Wang Qiang say?

10:30.590 --> 10:32.270
He asked me to ask you,

10:32.290 --> 10:34.330
besides taking naked photos of Lu Yan,

10:35.030 --> 10:35.870
is there anything else

10:35.890 --> 10:37.010
you want to do to her?

10:37.670 --> 10:38.860
If there are any,

10:39.120 --> 10:39.950
it's a separate charge.

10:41.040 --> 10:42.370
Tell Wang Qiang

10:42.590 --> 10:44.000
he just needs to deal with Lu Yan.

10:44.150 --> 10:45.530
The rest is up to him.

10:46.240 --> 10:47.610
I have plenty of money,

10:48.300 --> 10:49.730
and I only care about the result.

10:51.630 --> 10:52.310
Okay.

10:52.700 --> 10:53.680
Just deal with Lu Yan.

10:54.030 --> 10:54.890
Don't worry.

10:54.910 --> 10:56.460
I'll talk to him later.

10:57.010 --> 10:57.510
Jing.

10:57.540 --> 10:58.990
I'm going to the bathroom.

11:12.190 --> 11:13.120
Tell Wang Qiang

11:13.640 --> 11:15.170
he just needs to deal with Lu Yan.

11:15.200 --> 11:16.560
The rest is up to him.

11:22.360 --> 11:23.000
Senior.

11:23.110 --> 11:23.990
This residential environment

11:24.020 --> 11:24.860
seems quite chaotic.

11:27.920 --> 11:28.580
Is it here?

11:28.600 --> 11:29.160
Captain Jiang.

11:29.190 --> 11:29.820
Yue.

11:31.140 --> 11:32.050
What's going on?

11:32.920 --> 11:33.840
The landlord said

11:33.870 --> 11:35.310
there's a tenant that came in this afternoon

11:35.410 --> 11:37.100
who looks very similar to our portrait.

11:40.000 --> 11:40.650
Which unit?

11:40.820 --> 11:41.510
Upstairs.

11:41.670 --> 11:42.390
203.

11:45.670 --> 11:46.860
Have you checked her identity?

11:46.890 --> 11:48.060
Yes, it's a fake identity.

11:49.270 --> 11:50.140
What's wrong, Senior?

11:50.170 --> 11:51.050
Don't you want to go in and get a feel?

11:51.240 --> 11:51.710
No need.

11:52.870 --> 11:53.960
Watch over here.

11:54.000 --> 11:54.740
Wait for her to be back.

11:54.950 --> 11:55.360
Okay.

11:55.400 --> 11:56.020
Copy that.

12:12.260 --> 12:13.090
Mr. Wen,

12:13.300 --> 12:14.960
when will you give us a chance?

12:15.070 --> 12:16.450
There are so many artists in your company.

12:16.610 --> 12:17.670
You can give both our companies

12:17.690 --> 12:18.950
more endorsements.

12:19.810 --> 12:21.790
Our companies are also well-established.

12:21.910 --> 12:22.480
Sounds great.

12:22.560 --> 12:23.820
I'll get my staff

12:23.840 --> 12:24.670
to liaise with you.

12:24.730 --> 12:25.290
Okay.

12:26.360 --> 12:27.020
Look.

12:27.050 --> 12:28.520
We owe it to Mr. Wen's favor.

12:28.780 --> 12:29.330
Mr. Wen,

12:29.480 --> 12:30.510
if we collaborate,

12:30.770 --> 12:32.660
we’re willing to explore new avenues.

12:33.040 --> 12:33.480
Okay.

12:33.540 --> 12:34.750
I have faith in you.

12:34.990 --> 12:35.720
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

12:38.440 --> 12:39.940
What’s the conversation about? You seem so happy.

12:40.730 --> 12:41.710
Jing is here.

12:41.950 --> 12:43.010
We were hoping to leverage

12:43.080 --> 12:43.930
your influence

12:43.950 --> 12:46.270
to collaborate more with Mr. Wen.

12:47.190 --> 12:47.820
Yes.

12:47.840 --> 12:49.170
Please take care of us.

12:49.230 --> 12:50.360
The two of us

12:50.390 --> 12:51.200
bought a good amount

12:51.230 --> 12:52.360
of your company's porcelain today.

12:52.470 --> 12:53.060
Really?

12:53.080 --> 12:53.930
How supportive.

12:53.950 --> 12:54.730
No problem then.

12:54.750 --> 12:55.480
But you can't

12:55.480 --> 12:56.650
take my brand ambassador.

12:56.750 --> 12:57.550
Okay.

12:57.790 --> 12:59.290
You guys continue.

12:59.430 --> 13:00.980
We'll go over there and say hello.

13:01.000 --> 13:01.930
Okay, go ahead.

13:02.100 --> 13:02.610
Okay.

13:02.700 --> 13:03.350
See you, Mr. Liu.

13:03.390 --> 13:03.980
Bye.

13:05.610 --> 13:06.990
Bofeng is so handsome today.

13:07.040 --> 13:07.810
Thank you, Ms. Ding.

13:07.900 --> 13:09.190
You look great today, Ms. Ding.

13:09.210 --> 13:10.040
Thank you.

13:10.220 --> 13:11.970
We are very happy to work with you.

13:11.990 --> 13:13.200
Looking forward to a long-term collaboration.

13:13.250 --> 13:14.400
Well, I think you should thank

13:14.430 --> 13:15.590
my boss, Mr. Wen, for this collaboration.

13:15.610 --> 13:16.760
He is my boss.

13:17.120 --> 13:18.180
He has the final say.

13:18.210 --> 13:19.450
It has nothing to do with me.

13:19.580 --> 13:20.740
We only look at two factors.

13:20.950 --> 13:22.930
One is the product's legitimacy,

13:23.300 --> 13:24.070
and the other,

13:24.100 --> 13:24.920
is money.

13:24.940 --> 13:25.580
What a coincidence.

13:25.600 --> 13:26.410
I have both.

13:26.930 --> 13:27.880
Cheers to a pleasant partnership.

13:27.910 --> 13:28.600
Cheers.

13:31.670 --> 13:33.240
What projects has Bofeng been working on lately?

13:33.480 --> 13:34.600
There has been three or four productions.

13:34.810 --> 13:35.680
Among which, there's one

13:35.750 --> 13:36.940
which I especially liked.

13:37.020 --> 13:38.420
I asked Mr. Wen to help me

13:38.450 --> 13:39.430
get the role.

13:39.750 --> 13:41.080
The key is in his effort.

13:41.490 --> 13:42.760
-Wen!
-I’m rather curious...

13:44.090 --> 13:44.800
Tang Jie.

13:47.400 --> 13:48.670
Tang Jie is here too.

13:50.040 --> 13:50.960
Ms. Ding has put on

13:50.990 --> 13:52.150
quite a show here.

13:52.270 --> 13:53.790
Of course I must come.

13:54.410 --> 13:55.030
What's up?

13:55.250 --> 13:56.080
You don't welcome me?

13:57.270 --> 13:58.490
How could that be?

13:58.520 --> 13:59.790
We welcome you, of course.

14:00.060 --> 14:01.710
I know you love to be part of the action.

14:01.740 --> 14:03.290
Weren't you just like this in school?

14:04.670 --> 14:05.790
What do you mean?

14:05.820 --> 14:06.920
I don't understand.

14:07.190 --> 14:08.690
Have you forgotten?

14:08.960 --> 14:10.200
Don’t you remember how you

14:10.230 --> 14:11.340
followed Jiang Chengyi

14:11.390 --> 14:12.830
and Lu Yan around,

14:13.190 --> 14:14.530
becoming their third wheel?

14:19.580 --> 14:20.580
Their third wheel?

14:21.190 --> 14:21.950
Yes.

14:22.440 --> 14:23.790
But I think

14:23.810 --> 14:24.730
being a third wheel

14:24.830 --> 14:26.710
is better than being a bootlicker.

14:27.560 --> 14:29.050
Some people are really something.

14:29.120 --> 14:30.250
They've been sucking up for 8 years,

14:30.280 --> 14:31.630
but are somehow not tired of it.

14:31.740 --> 14:32.240
Indeed.

14:33.940 --> 14:34.900
Who are you talking about?

14:35.260 --> 14:37.440
I'm talking about whoever's talking to me.

14:38.790 --> 14:39.350
Ms. Ding.

14:39.370 --> 14:40.910
The signing ceremony is about to begin.

14:41.050 --> 14:41.490
Got it.

14:43.150 --> 14:44.210
I'm feeling good today,

14:44.250 --> 14:45.950
so I'll let it slide this time.

14:48.870 --> 14:50.030
What was that?

14:51.630 --> 14:52.400
Tang Jie.

14:52.420 --> 14:53.470
Have you seen Lu Yan?

14:54.120 --> 14:55.350
Lu Yan didn't say she was coming, did she?

14:55.370 --> 14:56.190
I have no idea.

14:56.750 --> 14:57.390
She's the one

14:57.430 --> 14:58.590
who asked me for an invitation.

14:58.690 --> 14:59.570
She said she would come.

15:01.140 --> 15:02.270
Maybe she had an urgent case to see to?

15:02.290 --> 15:03.250
I'll give her a call to ask.

15:04.780 --> 15:05.450
No need.

15:05.490 --> 15:06.690
No need.

15:07.480 --> 15:08.200
Let's go over first.

15:08.960 --> 15:10.030
Wen.

15:10.630 --> 15:11.360
Can I take a photo

15:11.390 --> 15:12.680
with Mr. Yu Bofeng?

15:15.640 --> 15:16.290
Sure.

15:18.080 --> 15:18.780
Let's take a selfie.

15:18.780 --> 15:19.120
Come.

15:19.150 --> 15:19.510
Okay.

15:24.990 --> 15:26.710
So handsome!

15:26.740 --> 15:27.310
Thank you.

15:30.920 --> 15:32.490
Come with me to check out the main stage.

15:53.750 --> 15:56.470
Next, we'll have the signing ceremony.

15:58.410 --> 16:00.030
-Great!
-Yes!

16:12.990 --> 16:16.480
[Signing Ceremony of Boya Porcelain's Spokesperson, Yu Bofeng]

16:14.350 --> 16:16.660
The signing ceremony had successfully concluded!

16:19.510 --> 16:20.570
Wishing us a pleasant partnership.

16:20.630 --> 16:21.480
Same here.

16:22.140 --> 16:23.750
Kindly have a commemorative photo.

16:31.260 --> 16:32.270
Let's welcome

16:32.310 --> 16:33.390
the organizer

16:33.470 --> 16:35.130
of this exchange conference,

16:35.270 --> 16:37.050
the founder of Boya Porcelain,

16:37.110 --> 16:38.050
Ms. Ding Jing,

16:38.140 --> 16:39.160
to give a speech!

16:39.190 --> 16:40.270
Let's give her a round of applause!

16:40.390 --> 16:41.880
Great!

16:44.150 --> 16:44.790
Thank you, thank you.

16:44.840 --> 16:46.150
Thank you, everybody.

16:46.370 --> 16:47.430
I deeply appreciate

16:47.470 --> 16:49.450
everyone's support for this conference.

16:49.910 --> 16:50.790
For the past six years...

16:57.710 --> 16:58.590
I'm sorry.

16:58.630 --> 16:59.720
A little hiccup.

17:00.230 --> 17:01.160
Over the past six years,

17:01.190 --> 17:02.870
our company has been dedicated to

17:02.890 --> 17:04.540
establishing a porcelain brand that represents

17:04.589 --> 17:06.480
a fresh take on traditional Chinese styles.

17:06.510 --> 17:07.240
We hope to

17:07.270 --> 17:08.640
attract more young people

17:08.670 --> 17:10.000
to like porcelain,

17:10.109 --> 17:11.150
and fall in love with porcelain.

17:11.410 --> 17:13.150
Today, our company

17:13.180 --> 17:14.750
has a big announcement to make.

17:14.980 --> 17:17.119
We've finally signed

17:17.190 --> 17:18.480
Mr. Yu Bofeng on.

17:19.030 --> 17:20.630
-Great!
-Nice!

17:27.960 --> 17:29.630
We'd also like to thank Mr. Wen

17:29.650 --> 17:31.540
for supporting our company over the years.

17:32.410 --> 17:33.220
Next,

17:33.270 --> 17:34.710
I would like to invite everyone

17:34.740 --> 17:36.420
to join me in enjoying

17:36.440 --> 17:38.290
our first promotional video.

17:40.370 --> 17:43.820
[Ninghai International Cultural and Artwork Exchange Conference]

17:44.670 --> 17:45.430
Let go of me!

17:45.510 --> 17:46.240
I have no idea

17:46.270 --> 17:47.460
what you're talking about.

17:48.060 --> 17:48.660
Jing.

17:48.690 --> 17:49.390
Are we

17:49.390 --> 17:50.280
being followed?

17:50.310 --> 17:51.510
Should we call the police?

17:51.630 --> 17:53.360
What should we do, Jing?

17:53.390 --> 17:54.640
Nonsense!

17:55.310 --> 17:56.950
Ms. Ding is actually a bully.

17:57.420 --> 17:58.220
That's right.

18:00.490 --> 18:01.850
T-Turn it off!

18:01.950 --> 18:02.800
What are you doing?

18:06.700 --> 18:08.550
How can you work with someone like that?

18:08.550 --> 18:09.560
Yes.

18:12.840 --> 18:14.320
I'm so sorry.

18:14.350 --> 18:15.510
There must be a misunderstanding.

18:16.530 --> 18:17.240
Stop looking.

18:17.270 --> 18:18.030
It's a waste of time.

18:18.070 --> 18:19.470
I'll just tell you, alright?

18:19.490 --> 18:20.670
Yes, I did bully her.

18:20.810 --> 18:21.780
So what?

18:22.090 --> 18:23.000
She washed my clothes

18:23.030 --> 18:23.600
and shoes,

18:23.630 --> 18:24.840
and had even knelt down before me.

18:25.510 --> 18:26.760
That's because she's timid

18:26.780 --> 18:27.320
and incompetent.

18:27.350 --> 18:28.170
She's a coward!

18:28.190 --> 18:29.370
What does it have to do with me?

18:30.330 --> 18:32.400
Let me tell you one last time.

18:33.160 --> 18:35.000
Her death has nothing to do with me.

18:35.430 --> 18:37.640
She brought it on herself.

18:39.320 --> 18:40.290
Lu Yan.

18:40.950 --> 18:41.870
Has it ever occurred to you

18:41.870 --> 18:43.380
that you're a jinx?

18:44.760 --> 18:45.710
Has anyone around you

18:45.710 --> 18:47.120
ever met a good end?

18:48.480 --> 18:49.680
I honestly think that,

18:49.840 --> 18:51.830
if it were up to me,

18:51.990 --> 18:53.900
your death would be the best outcome for everyone.

19:10.410 --> 19:11.170
Ding Jing.

19:17.760 --> 19:19.100
Yes, I did bully her.

19:19.350 --> 19:20.260
So what?

19:20.680 --> 19:22.390
Ding Jing, you bastard!

19:22.600 --> 19:23.860
I'll get even with her now.

19:23.910 --> 19:24.510
No.

19:24.540 --> 19:25.690
Don't be so anxious.

19:25.840 --> 19:26.550
I have a plan

19:26.590 --> 19:27.390
that I could use your help with.

19:27.430 --> 19:28.030
Tell me.

19:28.500 --> 19:30.010
I will do anything as long as

19:30.400 --> 19:31.610
she gets punished.

19:32.050 --> 19:33.030
She washed my clothes

19:33.070 --> 19:33.610
and shoes,

19:33.640 --> 19:34.650
and had even knelt down before me.

19:34.720 --> 19:35.900
That's because she's timid

19:35.930 --> 19:36.590
and incompetent.

19:36.680 --> 19:37.460
She's a coward!

19:37.480 --> 19:38.650
What does it have to do with me?

19:39.630 --> 19:40.620
Liu Yujie.

19:40.960 --> 19:42.630
I want to speak to you regarding

19:43.600 --> 19:44.850
Deng Man's incident.

19:46.350 --> 19:47.250
Do you realize now

19:47.280 --> 19:48.530
that you're on your own?

19:50.010 --> 19:51.350
You know very well

19:51.390 --> 19:52.510
what kind of person Ding Jing is.

19:53.370 --> 19:54.440
If you're going to

19:54.470 --> 19:55.430
continue being like this,

19:56.090 --> 19:57.540
no one can help you.

19:57.990 --> 19:59.130
You'll get involved too.

20:01.790 --> 20:02.640
Actually,

20:05.680 --> 20:07.250
Jiang Chengyi came to see me before.

20:08.380 --> 20:09.110
He...

20:09.310 --> 20:10.260
He came to see you?

20:10.950 --> 20:12.660
The incidents involving

20:14.120 --> 20:15.160
Wang Qiang stalking

20:15.190 --> 20:16.490
and photographing you

20:19.660 --> 20:21.570
were on the orders of Ding Jing.

20:28.950 --> 20:30.310
Can you do me a favor?

20:31.320 --> 20:32.790
I'll tell you what to do.

20:43.200 --> 20:44.570
I got the recording.

20:45.550 --> 20:46.960
Give it to Jiang Chengyi.

20:47.040 --> 20:48.860
It will prove your innocence.

20:49.100 --> 20:50.560
A-Aren't you leaving?

20:51.390 --> 20:52.560
I...

20:53.280 --> 20:54.730
I have something else to do.

20:55.510 --> 20:56.400
Thank you.

21:01.330 --> 21:02.000
Dalu.

21:02.100 --> 21:02.540
How is it?

21:02.560 --> 21:03.480
The backstage crew is all on our side.

21:03.510 --> 21:03.950
Don't worry.

21:03.970 --> 21:04.590
No one can come in.

21:15.190 --> 21:15.910
It's done.

21:21.150 --> 21:23.030
Lu Yan, what are you doing?

21:26.490 --> 21:28.190
I want you to pay the price.

21:29.350 --> 21:30.590
You bullied your classmates

21:30.610 --> 21:31.790
and drove your friend to death.

21:31.900 --> 21:33.030
You did so many bad things.

21:33.070 --> 21:34.410
How do you even sleep at night?

21:35.010 --> 21:36.230
You even hired someone to stalk me

21:36.270 --> 21:37.150
and take photos of me.

21:38.740 --> 21:39.900
Don't talk nonsense.

21:39.930 --> 21:41.170
Don't you slander me!

21:41.330 --> 21:42.670
All of you saw it, right?

21:43.040 --> 21:44.770
It's all on the screen.

21:44.960 --> 21:46.520
Why are you still making excuses?

21:46.730 --> 21:47.990
Today, I'll let everyone know

21:48.030 --> 21:49.530
what kind of person you are.

21:59.200 --> 22:00.750
A slap is nothing compared to what you deserve.

22:00.780 --> 22:01.800
If I had known

22:01.830 --> 22:02.830
you had been bullying Deng Man,

22:03.300 --> 22:04.730
I'd have torn your mouth apart.

22:15.550 --> 22:16.690
Stop shooting!

22:16.720 --> 22:17.800
What are you shooting?

22:18.270 --> 22:18.870
Don't...

22:18.890 --> 22:19.700
Don't hit him! Watch out!

22:19.730 --> 22:20.670
Watch out.

22:21.290 --> 22:22.030
Ms. Ding.

22:23.450 --> 22:24.130
I'm sorry.

22:24.450 --> 22:25.930
As per the contract,

22:26.630 --> 22:27.710
it’s you who have violated the terms.

23:12.940 --> 23:13.630
Stop!

23:18.070 --> 23:18.710
Hold her down!

23:18.750 --> 23:19.550
I've got her!

23:27.680 --> 23:28.440
Get up.

23:29.140 --> 23:30.430
Take off your hat.

23:30.450 --> 23:31.330
Take off your mask.

23:34.940 --> 23:35.790
What's your name?

23:37.940 --> 23:39.250
He's asking you. What’s your name?

23:39.680 --> 23:40.600
Zhou Fang.

23:41.700 --> 23:42.780
What’s this?

23:48.590 --> 23:49.140
Captain Jiang.

23:49.160 --> 23:50.340
I've searched the room.

23:50.360 --> 23:51.450
She's a dealer who specializes

23:51.480 --> 23:52.710
in selling antiques.

23:54.370 --> 23:55.510
Is this yours?

23:56.640 --> 23:57.290
Yes.

23:57.590 --> 23:58.070
Yes?

23:58.550 --> 23:59.040
Okay.

23:59.150 --> 23:59.990
Take her back.

24:00.240 --> 24:00.710
Let's go.

24:04.940 --> 24:06.260
Sihan,

24:06.390 --> 24:07.970
when we look for leads in the future,

24:08.070 --> 24:09.420
try to verify it first.

24:09.750 --> 24:10.470
Got it, Yue.

24:10.900 --> 24:12.320
Fortunately, we've found something that

24:12.340 --> 24:13.590
could be of help to other departments.

24:14.680 --> 24:15.590
What's wrong, Senior?

24:16.040 --> 24:17.170
Send this case back to the station,

24:17.310 --> 24:17.950
and then go home.

24:18.420 --> 24:19.020
We're done here.

24:19.140 --> 24:19.510
Let's go.

24:20.240 --> 24:20.730
Let's go.

24:22.570 --> 24:23.940
I've never seen something this expensive before.

24:26.430 --> 24:27.700
You're leaving, Senior?

24:28.510 --> 24:29.250
Bye.

24:38.310 --> 24:39.320
Are you home?

24:51.570 --> 24:52.260
That was gratifying.

24:52.610 --> 24:53.390
I feel great!

24:53.640 --> 24:55.170
Today, the two of us

24:55.180 --> 24:56.450
worked hand in hand

24:56.480 --> 24:57.780
to deliver justice.

24:57.850 --> 24:58.390
Indeed.

24:58.410 --> 24:59.590
Looking at what you did back there,

24:59.620 --> 25:00.870
you were really something.

25:01.530 --> 25:02.750
You scared me.

25:05.590 --> 25:07.060
I even felt that the slap was delivered late.

25:07.090 --> 25:08.790
I should have slapped her back then.

25:16.260 --> 25:17.180
The recording...

25:17.210 --> 25:18.710
have you handled it?

25:20.560 --> 25:21.190
Yes.

25:21.220 --> 25:23.240
I don't want too many people to know that

25:23.270 --> 25:25.020
Man was bullied.

25:25.780 --> 25:26.430
Indeed.

25:27.390 --> 25:28.230
She's already gone.

25:28.260 --> 25:29.470
Let's not make any more accusations.

25:32.590 --> 25:33.340
Lu Yan.

25:34.750 --> 25:35.590
If Man knows

25:35.640 --> 25:36.980
you did this for her,

25:37.080 --> 25:38.330
I'm sure she'll be very pleased.

25:44.130 --> 25:46.240
Don’t tell Dazhong and Jiang Chengyi

25:46.270 --> 25:48.350
about what happened today.

25:48.380 --> 25:49.400
Why?

25:49.430 --> 25:52.280
My evidence collection process

25:52.380 --> 25:53.710
was especially inappropriate.

25:54.240 --> 25:56.300
Just like what Ding Jing did to me,

25:56.450 --> 25:57.470
I also stalked her

25:57.470 --> 25:58.440
and threatened her.

25:58.810 --> 26:00.310
How could that be the same?

26:00.350 --> 26:01.360
You're trying to get

26:01.390 --> 26:02.350
justice for Man.

26:04.030 --> 26:05.350
Actually, at that time,

26:05.390 --> 26:06.240
it's because I only had Deng Man's

26:06.270 --> 26:07.350
Weibo's secondary account.

26:07.380 --> 26:08.350
Even if I had showed that

26:08.390 --> 26:09.820
to the police,

26:09.900 --> 26:11.250
they wouldn't handle it.

26:11.280 --> 26:12.750
I was left with no choice.

26:13.830 --> 26:14.850
But...

26:14.880 --> 26:16.130
it's all for Deng Man.

26:19.830 --> 26:21.320
I remember Jiang Chengyi

26:21.350 --> 26:22.470
always used to say,

26:23.450 --> 26:25.290
"A just outcome

26:25.510 --> 26:27.220
achieved through unjust means

26:27.350 --> 26:28.950
is not true justice."

26:33.100 --> 26:34.060
That's true.

26:34.600 --> 26:36.240
What I did in this case was wrong.

26:38.400 --> 26:39.790
Huh? What?

26:39.800 --> 26:40.520
I don't understand.

26:41.310 --> 26:41.980
No.

26:42.010 --> 26:42.960
I only know

26:42.990 --> 26:44.230
Ding Jing bullied Deng Man,

26:44.250 --> 26:45.560
so she has to pay the price.

26:47.560 --> 26:48.650
However, I can keep it a secret.

26:53.110 --> 26:54.110
But there's something

26:54.150 --> 26:55.240
I don't understand.

26:55.280 --> 26:57.090
You see, even if Man was introverted,

26:57.280 --> 26:58.310
it's not to the extent that

26:58.350 --> 26:59.950
she would kneel down to Ding Jing.

27:03.040 --> 27:03.860
Indeed.

27:04.140 --> 27:06.130
Even if Man likes Jiang Chengyi,

27:06.160 --> 27:07.110
Ding Jing couldn't possibly

27:07.150 --> 27:08.190
threaten her like this.

27:09.380 --> 27:10.270
Could it be...

27:10.290 --> 27:12.060
Man had other secrets?

27:21.170 --> 27:21.810
Ding Jing.

27:22.620 --> 27:23.910
What are you doing?

27:23.950 --> 27:24.870
So disobedient.

27:25.430 --> 27:26.530
Give me the luggage.

27:28.550 --> 27:29.370
Ding Jing.

27:33.010 --> 27:33.980
So it's true?

27:34.510 --> 27:35.690
You bullied your classmates?

27:36.750 --> 27:37.430
Ding.

27:37.470 --> 27:38.490
Leave us alone!

27:41.000 --> 27:41.830
Say something.

27:42.910 --> 27:44.480
I can’t believe you actually did something like this.

27:44.910 --> 27:46.350
Is this what I taught you?

27:46.790 --> 27:47.730
You know what?

27:47.950 --> 27:49.430
Many of my partners are going to

27:49.950 --> 27:51.200
terminate their contracts with me!

27:51.220 --> 27:52.710
You've thoroughly embarrassed me!

27:52.880 --> 27:53.990
Stop scolding, Ding.

27:56.740 --> 27:57.830
What did you say?

27:59.050 --> 28:00.600
You said you taught me.

28:02.970 --> 28:04.720
Now you think I'm embarrassing you,

28:04.750 --> 28:05.430
right?

28:05.990 --> 28:06.660
Ding Jing.

28:06.690 --> 28:07.820
How can you speak to Dad this way?

28:07.850 --> 28:08.600
Watch your attitude.

28:09.760 --> 28:11.670
Am I wrong?

28:12.550 --> 28:14.280
Have you ever been home all these years?

28:14.630 --> 28:15.710
Have you ever cared about me?

28:17.040 --> 28:18.160
Have you ever asked me

28:18.190 --> 28:20.190
how my day was?

28:20.650 --> 28:21.970
All you care about

28:22.030 --> 28:23.970
is your business.

28:24.400 --> 28:26.080
It's all because of you

28:26.110 --> 28:27.440
that I became like this.

28:27.460 --> 28:28.340
What did you say?

28:28.350 --> 28:29.440
Ding Jing!

28:31.310 --> 28:32.640
Shut up!

28:37.550 --> 28:38.340
Fine.

28:38.920 --> 28:39.790
You two go ahead.

28:39.850 --> 28:40.610
I'll leave.

28:40.800 --> 28:41.510
I'm leaving.

28:48.610 --> 28:49.550
Ding Jing.

28:50.110 --> 28:50.670
Ding Jing!

29:09.310 --> 29:10.460
If anything happens to

29:10.870 --> 29:12.190
Lu Yan,

29:12.210 --> 29:13.610
I'll find to you first.

29:13.640 --> 29:15.020
Why are you still making excuses?

29:15.050 --> 29:16.390
Today, I'll let everyone know

29:16.430 --> 29:17.510
what kind of person you are.

29:17.530 --> 29:18.560
If I had known

29:18.590 --> 29:19.610
you had been bullying Deng Man,

29:19.650 --> 29:20.970
I'd have torn your mouth apart.

29:25.430 --> 29:27.180
I can’t believe you actually did something like this.

29:27.360 --> 29:28.940
Is this what I taught you?

29:29.400 --> 29:30.280
You know what?

29:30.530 --> 29:32.090
Many of my partners are going to

29:32.460 --> 29:33.760
terminate their contracts with me!

29:33.790 --> 29:35.450
You've thoroughly embarrassed me!

29:51.040 --> 29:53.220
[Unknown Number]

29:56.480 --> 29:57.390
What's the point of

29:57.390 --> 29:58.370
calling me now?

29:58.630 --> 30:00.170
Are you trying to warn me?

30:00.300 --> 30:00.840
Fine.

30:00.990 --> 30:02.160
Let me tell you.

30:02.400 --> 30:03.280
We both had a hand

30:03.310 --> 30:04.590
in that incident.

30:05.380 --> 30:06.350
If they

30:06.390 --> 30:07.610
want to destroy me,

30:07.960 --> 30:09.840
we're going down together.

30:16.830 --> 30:17.690
Lu Yan.

30:19.310 --> 30:21.290
I must kill you.

30:56.380 --> 30:57.670
[Jiang Chengyi]

31:03.700 --> 31:04.390
Just answer the call.

31:04.410 --> 31:05.240
Put it on speaker.

31:08.030 --> 31:08.680
Hello?

31:09.800 --> 31:11.010
Are you home?

31:12.900 --> 31:14.090
I’m at Tang Jie's.

31:15.030 --> 31:16.110
At Tang Jie’s?

31:18.010 --> 31:18.670
What’s wrong?

31:18.670 --> 31:19.910
I'm staying over for the night.

31:19.970 --> 31:20.730
What's the matter?

31:22.920 --> 31:23.640
I want...

31:23.720 --> 31:25.200
What’s wrong, Captain Jiang?

31:25.220 --> 31:27.210
Still checking up on her at this hour?

31:27.400 --> 31:27.970
No.

31:29.200 --> 31:30.010
Well...

31:31.050 --> 31:32.730
Don’t worry.

31:32.770 --> 31:34.250
Lu Yan is very safe

31:34.280 --> 31:35.190
with me.

31:35.230 --> 31:36.230
She'll stay here tonight.

31:38.570 --> 31:39.360
Okay, that's all.

31:39.390 --> 31:40.380
Bye.

31:40.910 --> 31:41.390
Hello?

31:55.370 --> 31:58.380
[Shin Kong Place]

32:11.210 --> 32:12.170
What's the matter?

32:15.910 --> 32:16.950
This is a recording of

32:16.990 --> 32:17.870
my conversation with Ding Jing.

32:19.400 --> 32:20.750
It contains evidence of her admitting to

32:21.020 --> 32:22.200
ordering Wang Qiang

32:22.330 --> 32:24.150
to stalk and take photos of Lu Yan.

32:27.760 --> 32:28.880
You went to see Ding Jing?

32:31.150 --> 32:32.040
Don't worry.

32:32.350 --> 32:33.710
She didn't realize I was recording.

32:36.170 --> 32:36.810
Okay.

32:38.030 --> 32:38.960
Go to the police station

32:38.990 --> 32:39.750
and make a statement.

32:40.300 --> 32:41.210
Captain Jiang,

32:41.870 --> 32:43.590
Lu Yan is a good girl.

32:45.360 --> 32:46.710
I hope you can treat her well.

32:48.290 --> 32:49.430
You met each other?

32:52.740 --> 32:53.410
By the way,

32:54.080 --> 32:55.440
during this period,

32:55.580 --> 32:57.240
you must protect Lu Yan well.

32:57.530 --> 32:58.690
Based on my understanding of Ding Jing,

32:59.560 --> 33:01.220
she won't give up so easily.

33:03.590 --> 33:04.470
Got it.

33:05.040 --> 33:05.860
You go ahead.

33:18.750 --> 33:22.130
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

33:25.480 --> 33:26.670
Tell Wang Qiang

33:27.040 --> 33:28.480
he just needs to deal with Lu Yan.

33:28.520 --> 33:29.810
The rest is up to him.

33:30.720 --> 33:32.110
I have plenty of money,

33:32.800 --> 33:34.230
and I only care about the result.

33:35.110 --> 33:35.840
Okay.

33:36.300 --> 33:37.180
Just deal with Lu Yan.

33:37.580 --> 33:38.410
Don't worry.

33:38.500 --> 33:40.030
I'll talk to him later.

33:42.020 --> 33:42.730
Qin Yue!

33:43.980 --> 33:44.720
Qin Yue!

33:45.550 --> 33:46.190
Senior.

33:48.230 --> 33:49.100
Talk to me instead.

33:51.340 --> 33:52.560
I've heard the recording.

33:52.760 --> 33:53.650
It's Ding Jing.

33:55.330 --> 33:56.470
Bring her back.

33:58.300 --> 34:00.970
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

34:06.600 --> 34:07.590
Da Zhong, hurry up.

34:07.630 --> 34:08.270
We're going to be late.

34:09.949 --> 34:10.639
-Yan.
-Yes, honey.

34:10.670 --> 34:11.150
Sorry.

34:11.230 --> 34:12.310
Something came up at work.

34:12.389 --> 34:13.070
Don't mention it.

34:13.090 --> 34:14.159
I can go by myself.

34:14.190 --> 34:15.420
I can ask the driver to drive you.

34:15.630 --> 34:16.449
No need.

34:16.480 --> 34:17.600
It's a direct ride from

34:17.620 --> 34:18.420
the subway station downstairs.

34:18.650 --> 34:19.110
Okay.

34:19.130 --> 34:19.670
Go ahead.

34:19.670 --> 34:20.530
We're leaving.

34:23.850 --> 34:25.110
Do you have a power bank?

34:25.190 --> 34:26.380
My phone is dead.

34:26.469 --> 34:27.360
Yes, in the car.

34:27.429 --> 34:28.290
Go get it for her.

34:28.400 --> 34:28.989
Forget it.

34:29.110 --> 34:29.820
That's too troublesome.

34:29.989 --> 34:30.590
I won't charge it.

34:30.610 --> 34:31.650
You two go ahead.

34:31.840 --> 34:32.830
See you then.

34:32.860 --> 34:33.870
Watch out for yourself.

34:53.790 --> 34:54.510
Hello,

34:54.530 --> 34:56.580
the number you've dialed is unavailable.

35:01.750 --> 35:02.400
Hello?

35:02.940 --> 35:03.390
Hello?

35:04.600 --> 35:05.340
Tang Jie.

35:06.100 --> 35:07.080
Well,

35:07.150 --> 35:07.990
where is Lu Yan?

35:08.400 --> 35:09.450
Why can’t I get through?

35:09.800 --> 35:11.040
The battery must be dead.

35:11.080 --> 35:13.270
Today is Man's death.

35:13.300 --> 35:14.650
Yan plans on going to the cemetery.

35:14.800 --> 35:16.030
Something came up on my side,

35:16.070 --> 35:16.790
so I can't go with her.

35:16.820 --> 35:17.910
She's taking the subway there,

35:17.930 --> 35:18.790
and had just left.

35:18.870 --> 35:20.240
She's taking the subway?

35:20.990 --> 35:21.780
Alright, I see.

35:30.160 --> 35:33.210
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

36:02.370 --> 36:06.210
[Subway]

36:10.860 --> 36:13.320
[Subway]

36:44.430 --> 36:47.110
[Trains]

38:37.070 --> 38:38.780
[Exit]

38:39.130 --> 38:39.790
Lu Yan!

38:51.270 --> 38:51.920
Lu Yan!

38:56.310 --> 38:56.910
Lu Yan!

38:57.410 --> 38:58.570
Get up. Hurry!

39:01.510 --> 39:02.340
Get up!
